I dedicated my life to that woman.

153
00:07:14.948 --> 00:07:17.017
I gave her my everything.

154
00:07:17.083 --> 00:07:20.220
So you were upset. emotional.

155
00:07:20.253 --> 00:07:21.621
And drunk.

156
00:07:21.721 --> 00:07:23.423
What happened after the argument?

157
00:07:23.490 --> 00:07:25.449
I went home. took a
few too many gummies.

158
00:07:25.450 --> 00:07:26.559
