159
00:07:26.593 --> 00:07:29.529
Did you talk to Bella this morning?

160
00:07:29.663 --> 00:07:31.031
No.

161
00:07:31.164 --> 00:07:34.059
I just woke up about an hour ago.

162
00:07:34.092 --> 00:07:36.061
So you woke up at noon. right?

163
00:07:36.094 --> 00:07:37.387
And then what?

164
00:07:37.420 --> 00:07:40.206
I came here to get some food and coffee.

165
00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:41.541
I didn't kill Bella.

166
00:07:41.608 --> 00:07:44.527
Yeah. I was upset. but...

167
00:07:48.481 --> 00:07:51.351
Here I am yelling at her.

168
00:07:51.418 --> 00:07:54.387
