That's Marco.

180
00:08:27.153 --> 00:08:29.647
I don't know his last
name. He's a photographer.

181
00:08:29.714 --> 00:08:32.217
Any chance this was a
romantic relationship?

182
00:08:32.283 --> 00:08:33.927
Sure. it's possible.

183
00:08:33.960 --> 00:08:36.763
Guys were always flirting with Bella.

184
00:08:36.796 --> 00:08:38.498
Women too.

185
