to sleep with other people.

191
00:08:53.113 --> 00:08:58.017
♪ ♪

192
00:09:03.348 --> 00:09:04.991
We weren't arguing.

193
00:09:05.024 --> 00:09:07.026
We were just talking.

194
00:09:07.093 --> 00:09:09.287
It looked pretty intense to me.

195
00:09:09.354 --> 00:09:10.797
I understand how you might think that.

196
00:09:10.830 --> 00:09:12.632
I tend to wave my arms and hands a lot.

197
00:09:12.732 --> 00:09:14.200
I'm Colombian.

198
00:09:14.300 --> 00:09:15.869
And I'm Irish. and he's...

199
00:09:15.969 --> 00:09:17.504
- Nigerian.
- Yeah. so there you go.

200
00:09:17.604 --> 00:09:20.707
I had nothing to do with Bella's death.

201
00:09:20.708 --> 00:09:21.774
Then answer the question.

202
00:09:21.775 --> 00:09:23.276
What were you guys talking about?

203
00:09:23.343 --> 00:09:25.211
Bella didn't think that
I was attracted to her

204
00:09:25.311 --> 00:09:27.038
and that I was sleeping with
her for business reasons.

205
00:09:27.138 --> 00:09:29.307
and I got upset. told
her I couldn't have been

206
00:09:29.308 --> 00:09:31.384
- more attracted to her.
- Then what?

207
00:09:31.451 --> 00:09:34.220
After she jumped in
the SUV and drove off?

208
00:09:34.287 --> 00:09:37.424
I got a cab. went to her place.

209
00:09:37.457 --> 00:09:39.025
and we spent the night together.

210
00:09:39.058 --> 00:09:40.260
And in the morning?

211
00:09:40.326 --> 00:09:43.663
- I woke up around 9:00 or so.
- You see Bella?

212
00:09:43.763 --> 00:09:46.466
No. she already left.

213
00:09:46.533 --> 00:09:48.368
She liked to take early morning walks.

214
00:09:48.401 --> 00:09:49.769
And what did you do?

215
00:09:49.803 --> 00:09:51.271
I hung out. made a cappuccino.

216
00:09:51.337 --> 00:09:52.530
read a few emails. Then I went home.

217
00:09:52.564 --> 00:09:54.007
Yeah? Around what time?

218
00:09:54.107 --> 00:09:55.708
9:30. 9:45.

219
00:09:55.809 --> 00:09:57.577
You aware of any problems she might have

220
00:09:57.644 --> 00:10:00.213
been experiencing in her
personal or professional life?

221
00:10:00.313 --> 00:10:02.574
No.

222
00:10:02.674 --> 00:10:04.517
I can't believe Bella's really dead.

223
00:10:04.584 --> 00:10:07.086
I know. It's terrible.

224
00:10:07.187 --> 00:10:08.822
Yeah.

225
00:10:08.922 --> 00:10:12.092
On top of that. she was
my most important client.

226
00:10:16.421 --> 00:10:19.757
Unfortunately. surveillance
video confirms Marco's alibi.

227
00:10:19.858 --> 00:10:23.236
He didn't leave Bella's
apartment until 9:40.

228
00:10:23.269 --> 00:10:25.004
Why do you say unfortunately?

229
00:10:25.071 --> 00:10:26.998
I didn't care for that dude. Mm-mm.

230
00:10:27.065 --> 00:10:30.376
Okay. so what you're saying.
really. is we have nothing.

231
00:10:30.477 --> 00:10:32.078
It's early.

232
00:10:32.112 --> 00:10:33.947
Well. tell that to the guys over at 1PP.

233
00:10:34.047 --> 00:10:35.081
