234
00:10:35.181 --> 00:10:36.708
We're trying.

235
00:10:36.774 --> 00:10:38.551
Okay. why don't you check
out the husband again?

236
00:10:38.651 --> 00:10:40.353
- Tate Harris?
- Mm-hmm.

237
00:10:40.453 --> 00:10:42.622
I mean. I know he says he
was in Pound Ridge the morning

238
00:10:42.722 --> 00:10:44.716
