to have sex with other men.

240
00:10:47.293 --> 00:10:48.294
Well. like him or not.

241
00:10:48.394 --> 00:10:49.462
it appears he was home all morning.

242
00:10:49.562 --> 00:10:50.563
How do you know?

243
00:10:50.597 --> 00:10:51.798
The house across the street

244
00:10:51.898 --> 00:10:53.233
has three surveillance
cameras staring straight

245
00:10:53.333 --> 00:10:55.201
at Tate and Bella's home.

246
00:10:55.268 --> 00:10:57.737
There's no video of Tate
coming or going the night before

247
00:10:57.837 --> 00:11:00.740
