through that front door.

248
00:11:00.840 --> 00:11:03.543
Phone company just gave
us Bella's electronic info.

249
00:11:03.643 --> 00:11:06.012
- Anything?
- Maybe.

250
00:11:06.045 --> 00:11:07.780
Looks like she texted
some guy named Ellis

251
00:11:07.781 --> 00:11:09.207
three days before the murder.

252
00:11:09.274 --> 00:11:12.452
She said. "I can't believe
Trey did this to me."

253
00:11:12.485 --> 00:11:13.953
And she follows up with.

254
00:11:14.053 --> 00:11:16.648
"I want to destroy that bastard."

255
00:11:16.748 --> 00:11:19.450
With five exclamation points.

256
00:11:19.484 --> 00:11:20.910
Chase it down.

257
00:11:22.929 --> 00:11:26.558
I was Bella's personal
attorney for 11 years.

258
00:11:26.624 --> 00:11:29.460
We texted back and
forth quite frequently.

259
00:11:29.494 --> 00:11:31.004
We know that. Mr. Matz.

260
00:11:31.070 --> 00:11:33.064
What we don't know
is what Bella meant by

261
00:11:33.131 --> 00:11:35.333
"I can't believe Trey did this to me"

