00:34:09.828 --> 00:34:12.322
What the hell are you trying to do?

778
00:34:12.355 --> 00:34:14.032
This some sort of joke?

779
00:34:14.099 --> 00:34:17.102
Your client invited four
female friends to a party

780
00:34:17.168 --> 00:34:18.904
at Dutch Wilmont's apartment.

781
00:34:18.970 --> 00:34:20.672
She supplied them with illegal drugs

782
00:34:20.739 --> 00:34:22.974
