powerful film producer.

785
00:34:28.346 --> 00:34:30.148
Those women are my friends.

786
00:34:30.181 --> 00:34:32.684
They're not hookers.

787
00:34:32.751 --> 00:34:34.786
So what? We like to have sex. Who cares?

788
00:34:34.886 --> 00:34:36.454
That is how we choose to live our life.

789
00:34:36.555 --> 00:34:37.856
I'm not judging you.

790
00:34:37.889 --> 00:34:39.491
I couldn't care less what
you do with your time.

791
00:34:39.557 --> 00:34:44.429
But you need to testify.

792
00:34:44.529 --> 00:34:47.065
We are done here.

793
00:34:47.165 --> 00:34:54.072
♪ ♪

794
00:34:59.778 --> 00:35:01.513
