798
00:35:07.452 --> 00:35:11.489
Yeah. well. there's a reason for that.

799
00:35:11.556 --> 00:35:12.991
What do you mean?

800
00:35:13.058 --> 00:35:15.360
She's not a sex trafficker.

801
00:35:15.393 --> 00:35:18.463
Come on. Nolan. we both know
this isn't sex trafficking.

802
00:35:18.530 --> 00:35:21.533
It's just a bunch of consenting
adults doing drugs. having sex.

803
00:35:21.566 --> 00:35:23.368
Her actions on the night in question

804
00:35:23.401 --> 00:35:26.404
