in New York State penal law.

805
00:35:26.438 --> 00:35:29.608
Don't do all that. Okay? Not with me.

806
00:35:29.708 --> 00:35:30.775
Okay.

807
00:35:32.577 --> 00:35:34.412
- Let's say I agree with you.
- Mm-hmm.

808
00:35:34.479 --> 00:35:37.015
It was just a wild
night in the big city.

809
00:35:37.115 --> 00:35:38.650
That doesn't give her the right

810
00:35:38.750 --> 00:35:42.278
