811
00:35:42.345 --> 00:35:45.156
or to duck her legal responsibilities

812
00:35:45.256 --> 00:35:48.526
so that she can avoid embarrassment

813
00:35:48.593 --> 00:35:51.421
and preserve her marriage
to some film director.

814
00:35:51.454 --> 00:35:52.964
And I agree with you.

815
00:35:53.064 --> 00:35:55.583
But to threaten her with
sex trafficking charges?

816
00:35:55.617 --> 00:35:57.102
Come on. Nolan.

817
00:35:57.168 --> 00:36:00.263
My job is to put Tate Harris
away for the rest of his life.

818
00:36:00.296 --> 00:36:02.140
And if the cost of doing that is

819
00:36:02.207 --> 00:36:05.944
blowing up some selfish actress.

820
00:36:05.977 --> 00:36:09.372
I can live with that.

821
00:36:09.439 --> 00:36:11.483
Your call.

822
00:36:11.549 --> 00:36:13.752
Don't get all high and mighty here.

823
00:36:13.785 --> 00:36:14.919
Why not?

824
00:36:14.986 --> 00:36:16.588
You're selfish too.

825
00:36:16.654 --> 00:36:18.456
Excuse me?

826
00:36:18.490 --> 00:36:21.276
You're leveraging Grace to win the trial

827
00:36:21.309 --> 00:36:24.387
to make yourself feel good.
to advance your career.

828
00:36:24.454 --> 00:36:27.599
The only thing I'm leveraging is the law

829
00:36:27.632 --> 00:36:30.168
to get justice for Bella Ross.

830
00:36:30.235 --> 00:36:33.396
[PHONE BUZZING]

831
00:36:33.463 --> 00:36:35.131
Nolan Price.

832
00:36:37.342 --> 00:36:39.928
Hey. I'll see you both
in court tomorrow morning.

833
00:36:42.781 --> 00:36:44.883
