837
00:36:55.960 --> 00:36:58.096
January 21st of this year.

838
00:36:58.196 --> 00:37:00.632
- Was anyone else there?
- Yes.

839
00:37:00.665 --> 00:37:02.033
Seven other people.

840
00:37:02.100 --> 00:37:04.803
