848
00:37:25.090 --> 00:37:26.674
Yes. I saw him do both.

849
00:37:26.708 --> 00:37:30.061
When he exited the closet.
was he carrying anything?

850
00:37:34.566 --> 00:37:37.627
He was holding something
wrapped up in a T-shirt.

851
00:37:37.694 --> 00:37:38.837
I asked him about it.

852
00:37:38.903 --> 00:37:40.538
Well. more like joked.

853
00:37:40.572 --> 00:37:43.900
I said it looked like he
was stealing something.

854
00:37:43.967 --> 00:37:46.978
- Did he respond?
- He said. "I am."

855
00:37:47.045 --> 00:37:48.905
I just thought he was kidding.

856
00:37:48.972 --> 00:37:50.582
Nothing further.

857
00:37:52.876 --> 00:37:54.752
Ms. Burke. you're an actress?

858
00:37:54.819 --> 00:37:56.254
Yes.

859
00:37:56.354 --> 00:38:00.041
Married to Arthur Burke.
the acclaimed film director.

860
00:38:00.074 --> 00:38:01.359
Yes.

861
00:38:01.426 --> 00:38:04.062
On January 21st. you attended a party

862
00:38:04.129 --> 00:38:07.098
at Dutch Wilmont's apartment and had sex

863
00:38:07.165 --> 00:38:08.391
with Tate Harris. correct?

864
00:38:10.668 --> 00:38:11.668
Yes.

865
00:38:11.703 --> 00:38:14.272
Were you drinking that evening?

866
00:38:14.339 --> 00:38:15.473
Yes.

867
00:38:15.573 --> 00:38:19.377
Were you under the
influence of any narcotics?

868
00:38:19.511 --> 00:38:21.212
Yes.

869
00:38:21.346 --> 00:38:27.010
Yet you somehow saw Tate
Harris carrying something

870
00:38:27.076 --> 00:38:28.253
