871
00:38:28.286 --> 00:38:32.557
Was this before or after you had sex?

872
00:38:32.690 --> 00:38:34.017
After.

873
00:38:34.117 --> 00:38:36.794
Before or after you were
drinking and doing drugs?

874
00:38:36.861 --> 00:38:37.962
After.

875
00:38:38.029 --> 00:38:41.232
So you're saying Tate Harris just

876
00:38:41.266 --> 00:38:44.294
walked into Dutch Wilmont's closet.

877
00:38:44.360 --> 00:38:45.904
stole a gun right before your eyes

878
00:38:45.937 --> 00:38:47.572
like there was no care in the world.

879
00:38:47.605 --> 00:38:49.507
He thought I was asleep. and I was.

880
00:38:49.607 --> 00:38:51.201
But then I heard him rummaging around.

881
00:38:51.301 --> 00:38:52.944
so I woke up.

882
00:38:52.977 --> 00:38:54.746
In exchange for your testimony today.

883
00:38:54.779 --> 00:38:57.515
Mr. Price promised not to file

884
00:38:57.615 --> 00:39:00.752
