885
00:39:00.818 --> 00:39:02.687
Yes. that's correct.

886
00:39:02.754 --> 00:39:04.689
Are you a pimp. Ms. Burke?

887
00:39:04.756 --> 00:39:08.159
No. I am definitely not a pimp.

888
00:39:08.226 --> 00:39:10.028
[TENSE MUSIC]

889
00:39:10.094 --> 00:39:11.454
Nothing further.

890
00:39:14.157 --> 00:39:15.366
Redirect. Your Honor.

891
00:39:15.433 --> 00:39:18.286
Ms. Burke. did my decision

892
00:39:18.319 --> 00:39:20.672
